              "kind": "output",
              "text": "ValueError: all the input arrays must have same number of dimensions, but"
            },
            {
              "kind": "output",
              "text": "the array at index 0 has 2 dimension(s) and the array at index 1 has 1"
            },
            {
              "kind": "output",
              "text": "dimension(s)"
